# Development Workflow

## Commands
```bash
npm run dev              # Web + worker with hot-reload
npm run dev:web          # Web server only
npm run dev:worker       # Worker only
npm run test             # Jest watch mode
npm run eslint           # Lint and auto-fix
npm run update-env       # Pull secrets from Doppler
```

## Code Style
- Print width: 120, tab width: 2 spaces
- Single quotes JS/TS, double quotes JSX
- Trailing commas, semicolons required
- Files: camelCase for JS, PascalCase for React components

## Don't
- Use `var` (use `const`/`let`)
- Use `console.log` (use logger)
- Hardcode config values
- Commit .env files
